.mdl-card(id='iconcard')
  h4 Survey Icon
  form.iconupload(enctype='multipart/form-data' action='/studies/icon/' + studyId)
    p.
      The survey icon will be used as an App Store icon, iOS application icon,
      and web application icon. The icon must be 1024x1024 pixel size.
      You can also drag and drop files anywhere on this page to start uploading.
    img.iconimg(id='iconimg', src='/src/studies/assets/app-icon.png')
    input(id='fileElement', type='file', name='file', accept='image/png', style='opacity: 0', onchange="edit.handleFiles(this.files)")
    button.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button(id='fileSelect', action='/studies/' + studyId) Choose file
